- **Post-Production:** Editing, audio mastering, color grading, branding element insertion  
- **Review:** Multi-division review including ENGINEERING, MARKETING, and SCIENCE for content accuracy and alignment  
- **Final Polish:** MUSE final audio-visual enhancement and readiness for publishing  


### 2.2 Tools and Technologies  
- Audio recorded and mixed with frequency layering tools supporting 528Hz fundamental tone  
- Video editing suite configured with FFPMA brand color palettes calibrated for deep blue, cyan, and gold fidelity  
- Version control and asset management integrated via Google Drive and internal platforms ensuring seamless collaboration  


