- Pink hues avoided entirely to maintain brand consistency and message integrity.  
- Visual transitions are smooth and support flowing energy motifs consistent with healing themes (DNA helices, energy waves).  
- Spelling and grammatical review yielded zero errors, complying fully with PMA language compliance standards.  


